usage: epub [-h] [-d] EPUB

python/curses epub reader. Requires BeautifulSoup

Keyboard commands:
    Esc/q          - quit
    Tab/Left/Right - toggle between TOC and chapter views
    TOC view:
        Up         - up a line
        Down       - down a line
        PgUp       - up a page
        PgDown     - down a page
    Chapter view:
        Up         - up a page
        Down       - down a page
        PgUp       - up a line
        PgDown     - down a line

positional arguments:
  EPUB        view EPUB

optional arguments:
  -h, --help  show this help message and exit
  -d, --dump  dump EPUB to text
  -n, --night start in night mode(light letters on dark background)
